item.title: Content Writing
item.description: OpenDroid Wiki: Building android is very complex, needing a lot of expertise, calmness of mind, and a non-insignificant understanding of how these devices function. I contributed to early documentation(especially helping with Crave.io related documentation) and maintain a good chunk of this at the time of writing.
